Text: Thank you so very much, rkstr! Merry Christmas!
rkstr, you are a gentleman and a scholar.  Thank you!
Well, rkstr... it's December 22nd, an' yer still postin' vids - the world truly didn't end!  Thanks for your hard work all year, and if I knew where to send the holiday jam basket... I would.
Happy Holidays to you and yours!
